\Phi_k(r) = Cr^{-\frac{1}{2}}J_{-\frac{1}{2}}(kr),
C = c_1-c_2
\Phi_k(r) = Cr^{-\frac{1}{2}}\sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi kr}}\cos(kr) = -C'(k)\frac{\cos(kr)}{kr} = C'(k)y_0(kr).
